14:10.250 --> 14:13.120
[chatter]

14:13.153 --> 14:14.955
Alright, guys.

14:14.988 --> 14:16.423
Guys.

14:16.456 --> 14:18.258
Do you see nail polish?

14:18.291 --> 14:19.659
[chatter continues]

14:19.692 --> 14:22.062
Hello, guys! Guys.

14:22.095 --> 14:24.264
Turn around, c'mon,
class has started.

14:24.297 --> 14:26.967
