in one period.

14:35.208 --> 14:38.245
So, today, what I'm gonna do is
I'm gonna assign some roles,

14:38.278 --> 14:41.514
assign some scenes,
and then I'm gonna put
you guys into groups.

14:41.548 --> 14:44.084
Okay?
Here's how it's gonna work.

14:44.117 --> 14:46.519
The groups that are
the most rehearsed,

14:46.553 --> 14:49.622
