you guys that well,

14:53.260 --> 14:55.128
but I wanna get to know you.

14:55.162 --> 14:58.531
So, I'm just gonna
start assigning roles

14:58.565 --> 15:00.267
based on who wants to play what.

15:00.300 --> 15:02.302
Let's start with
Elizabeth Proctor.

15:02.335 --> 15:04.137
This is the wife
of the protagonist.

15:04.171 --> 15:05.939
She's accused of witchcraft.

15:05.973 --> 15:10.177
Any seniors wanna maybe
give this a shot?

15:13.013 --> 15:14.381
Okay, you're-- what's your name?

15:14.414 --> 15:15.548
Lily.

15:15.582 --> 15:16.950
Lily, want to give it a shot?

15:16.984 --> 15:19.419
-Sure.
-Great, thank you.

15:19.452 --> 15:21.354
Um, alright, moving down.

15:21.388 --> 15:22.689
Abigail Williams.

15:22.722 --> 15:26.426
Now, this is the villain
of the play, okay?

15:26.459 --> 15:28.428
It's a great role.

15:28.461 --> 15:31.098
She starts having an affair
with John Proctor

15:31.131 --> 15:34.067
and then,
when he wants to stop it,

15:34.101 --> 15:36.003
